casebody.data:
Terrell E. REYNOLDS, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81074 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: OCTOBER 23, 2018 Lisa M. Stroup, Saint Louis, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Gregory L. Barnes, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division Three: Anthony Rex Gabbert, Presiding Judge, Victor C. Howard, Judge, Alok Ahuja, Judge

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Terrell Reynolds appeals the circuit court's denial of his Rule 29.15 motion for post-conviction relief after an evidentiary hearing. We affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
